'''''Christie's Fine Printed Books and Manuscripts 24 May 2002''''' is an auction catalogue which includes three reproductions of letters from [[J.R.R. Tolkien]] to [[Nancy Smith]] and a joint manuscript ("[[Index questions]]").

*Lot 409 (pp. 278–9): "[[Index questions]]" and [[Letter to Nancy Smith (27 May 1958)]]
*Lot 410 (pp. 280–1): [[Letter to Nancy Smith (Christmas 1963)]]
*Lot 411 (p. 282): [[Letter to Nancy Smith (30 May 1966)]]
